 我地有好多有創意既宣傳手法，其中可以參考：<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Y0OsqvL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FY0OsqvL.jpg&h=1aadf202&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n方法：<br />\n<br />\n5-8個人圍成一圈，手上可以揸IPAD/NOTEBOOK/紙標語/傳單。<br />\n<br />\n對外原地站立，輪班制，企得耐就換人，休息。<br />\n<br />\n分散係機場唔同位置，唔好分散太遠，免得有事難支援。有事發生既話隨時流動，唔好死守一地方，散完再聚。<br />\n<br />\n一組最好有一兩個英文/外語好既人，方便同旅客解釋發生咩事。<br />\n<br />\n宣傳品可以放係附近，方便派發。"},{"pid":"6e94a7f6bf5758ad35a2cfd7f75d73e29504d80c","tid":1365372,"uid":62011,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T16:24:21.000Z","msg":"聲音可以參考：<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=jbF9rHSNFhM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DjbF9rHSNFhM&d=VlhNwxbPYDbrmmiZclZ9hBVENBC9VnKGSHAjWoGsWeM%3D&h=7dce38d7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=jbF9rHSNFhM</a>"},{"pid":"c6a9b39452c76f085fce853523ddf01495f29b34","tid":1365372,"uid":35790,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T16:24:28.000Z","msg":"記得攞埋727元朗恐襲<br />\n2個軍裝見死不救走頭片段"},{"pid":"573e568081c5e1bd2db724d9950b2a4d3ebc8a49","tid":1365372,"uid":197404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T16:28:01.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/iTIqDFPjypU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FiTIqDFPjypU&d=VlhNwxbPYDbrmmiZclZ9hBVENBC9VnKGSHAjWoGsWeM%3D&h=6267986b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/iTIqDFPjypU</a><br />\n法國記者<br />\nstop shooting journalists"},{"pid":"1d02fe917b8d3ab9c17368e3ae4af521e7ef3801","tid":1365372,"uid":266668,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T16:48:09.000Z","msg":"除咗播片仲有咩可以做？"},{"pid":"eaeef964f68efec89216c9af197c30b07e294b6d","tid":1365372,"uid":266668,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T16:48:24.000Z","msg":"機場派傳單得唔得？"},{"pid":"e4889d4a1ba20837e6a0d7618d8b1f3d4d73cb